                        to <title type="manuscript" corresp="#MSIX">MS IX</title> broadside; this drawing, therefore, like <ref type="figure" target="the_meuse_liege_drawing_msix.php"><title type="artwork" corresp="#JRTHEMEUSELIEGEMSIX">Li&#x00E8;ge</title></ref>, 
